            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Start on your hands and knees with your wrists directly under your shoulders and your knees directly under your hips.",
                    "Extend your right leg straight back behind you, keeping your toes tucked under and your foot flexed.",
                    "Engage your core and lift your right leg up towards the ceiling, keeping it straight and strong.",
                    "At the same time, lift your left arm up towards the ceiling, reaching it straight out in front of you.",
                    "Hold for a few breaths, then release and repeat on the other side."
                ]
